io.soabase.config.service

Interface ComposedConfigurationServiceFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ClientComposedConfigurationFactory, CuratorComposedConfigurationFactory, SoaComposedConfigurationFactory, SqlComposedConfigurationFactory

    public interface ComposedConfigurationServiceFactory
    Service/Bundles can provide an instance of this factory and add a service provider-configuration file. FromServices can then be used to generate a new ComposedConfiguration instance.
